article.headline: Southern Miss. 69, Spring Hill 49
article.story: BILOXI, Miss. -- In a Dec. 22 story about a men's basketball game between Southern Miss and Spring Hill, The Associated Press misidentified the leading scorers in the game. R.L. Horton scored 17 points and Andre Stephens had 14 points for Southern Miss, and Courtney Beasley and Craig Craft added 13 points apiece. Josh Barnes and Gustavo Lino of Southern Miss were incorrectly described as the two leading scorers.
